🫁 The Mechanism (simple version)
	•	Short lines → faster breath → urgency
	•	Long lines → slower breath → depth
	•	Spacing → forced pauses → reset
	•	Repetition → entrainment → rhythm lock

You’re basically doing:

text → breath → state

