🧩 How We Use This (BESPOKE Layer)

We can design writing that:

1. Induces calm
	•	longer lines
	•	soft breaks
	•	descending rhythm

⸻

2. Builds intensity
	•	shorter bursts
	•	tighter spacing
	•	stacking phrases

⸻

3. Creates control
	•	inhale cue (open line)
	•	exhale cue (longer line)
	•	pause (empty space)

